.TH SHORT 1 "March 2026" "Version 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
short \- sort lines of text files (optimized minimalist version)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B short
[\fIFILE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B short
sorts lines of text files in ascending order using optimized algorithms.
It reads all lines from the specified file, sorts them alphabetically,
and prints the result to standard output with minimal memory usage.
.SH OPTIONS
None.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP "short file.txt"
Sort lines in file.txt and print to stdout.
.SH AUTHOR
The JLC Project
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sort (1)